Kuffs;;1992;;PG-13;;Action,Comedy,Crime;;5.9;;Bruce A. Evans;;Christian Slater,Milla Jovovich,Ric Roman Waugh,Steve Holladay,Chad Randall,Clarke Coleman,Leon Rippy,Craig Benton,Ashley Judd,Bruce Boxleitner,Joshua Cadman,Mary Ellen Trainor,Aki Aleong,Henry G. Sanders,Dom Magwili,Kevin Leidich,E. Keith Polk,Susie Schelling;;George Kuffs didn't finish high-school, just lost his job and his girlfriend who still is in college is pregnant. Since he can't see how he can support her, he thinks she is better off without him. So he visits his elder brother, Brad, to squeze him for a loan so he can go to Brazil where there's a gold-rush going on. Unfortunately Brad is killed and George is suddenly the owner of Brad's "patrol special" district.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0104647/